milestones.description: Tanwir Afzal and Babar Hayat's 60-run partnership is HKG's highest for the 7th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 50 between Babar Hayat and Haseeb Amjad
Tony Ura and Vani Morea's 17-run partnership is PNG's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 8 between Assad Vala and Tony Ura
Assad Vala and Lega Siaka's 83-run partnership is PNG's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 65 between Geraint Jones and Lega Siaka
Babar Hayat has broken the record for most sixes (11) in ODIs for HKG, going past Haseeb Amjad's 8
Mahuru Dai has become the top wicket-taker for PNG in ODIs with 6 wickets, going past Norman Vanua's 4
Babar Hayat has scored 4 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for HKG breaking Anshy Rath's record
Babar Hayat has become the top scorer for HKG in ODIs with 343 runs, going past Anshy Rath's 308
Tony Ura has broken the record for most catches (3) in ODIs for PNG, going past Lega Siaka's 2
Mahuru Dai has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (3) for PNG, going past Charles Amini
Dogodo Bau has broken the record for most dismissals in an innings (3) in ODIs for PNG, going past Jack Vare's 2
